"""""""""" Add newline in normal mode with shift+enter
" Quickly insert an empty new line without entering insert mode
nnoremap L i<CR><Esc>
nnoremap <Leader>o i<CR><Esc>
nnoremap <Leader>O i<CR><Esc>

